00m short track final at Salt Lake City, winning Australia's first Winter Olympic gold.\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 600, \"end\": 608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"score\": 0.9999999926990313, \"rank\": 7.301131664983202e-09, \"text\": \"Bradbury\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\"}, {\"begin\": 675, \"end\": 689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"score\": 0.8449607239820853, \"rank\": 0.18348696172121953, \"text\": \"Salt Lake City\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\"}, {\"begin\": 699, \"end\": 708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999999631081671, \"rank\": 2.14579555253614e-08, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last man\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Twenty years later, he went into \\\"Olympic mode\\\" again to rescue four teenagers from rough seas at Caloundra.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 837, \"end\": 846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6546860330456592e-24, \"text\": \"Caloundra\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic mode\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"four teenagers\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 817}, {\"ngram\": \"rough seas\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His March 2022 heroics have officially been recognised after receiving a commendation for brave conduct from the Queensland governor in Brisbane.\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 962, \"end\": 981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Governor_of_Queensland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Queensland governor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Governor_of_Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Governor_of_Queensland\"}, {\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9999997584214108, \"rank\": 2.412839657417677e-07, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His March 2022 heroics\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"a commendation\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"brave conduct\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With the Olympic gold, I had been training my guts out for 14 years to get myself in that position,\\\" Mr Bradbury told AAP.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1101, \"end\": 1109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"score\": 0.9999999926990313, \"rank\": 7.301131664983202e-09, \"text\": \"Bradbury\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic gold\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"my guts\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"14 years\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1064}, {\"ngram\": \"that position\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"AAP\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not sure how you compare it with a bravery award.\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1176, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bravery award\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1175}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But it was nice to know that the body and the mind could switch back to Olympic mode for a few minutes when required.\\\"\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1297, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1216}, {\"ngram\": \"the mind\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1229}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic mode\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"a few minutes\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Bradbury was teaching his son how to surf in 2022 when he saw what he thought was a log in the huge swell.\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1302, \"end\": 1310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"score\": 0.9999999926990313, \"rank\": 7.301131664983202e-09, \"text\": \"Bradbury\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his son\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"a log\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"the huge swell\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then I realised it was a human head,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1457, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a human head\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I clicked straight into gear.\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gear\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I sent my son to the lifeguards and paddled out.\\\"\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my son\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"the lifeguards\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Bradbury first came across a 12-year-old girl.\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1544, \"end\": 1552, \"